---
import PageLayout from '../../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout
	title="332 Labs — 332 Projects"
	description="332 Labs — a unified platform for CTF challenges, courses, video and audio content, and more. Coming soon."
>
	<div class="page-root relative min-h-screen px-4 pb-32 pt-32">
		<div class="dot-pattern pointer-events-none absolute inset-0" aria-hidden="true"></div>

		<div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden" aria-hidden="true">
			<div
				class="absolute left-1/2 top-1/4 h-[700px] w-[700px] -translate-x-1/2 rounded-full"
				style="background: radial-gradient(circle, oklch(0.9 0 0 / 6%), transparent 65%); filter: blur(100px);"
			></div>
		</div>

		<div class="relative z-10 mx-auto max-w-4xl">

			<!-- Breadcrumb -->
			<nav class="mb-10" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
				<a
					href="/projects"
					class="glass-nav-link inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg px-3 py-1.5 text-sm tracking-wider text-muted-foreground transition-all hover:text-foreground no-underline"
				>
					<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-3.5 w-3.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
						<path d="m15 18-6-6 6-6"/>
					</svg>
					All Projects
				</a>
			</nav>

			<!-- Hero -->
			<div class="mb-16 text-center animate-[fade-in-up_0.7s_ease-out_both]">
				<div class="glass-card inline-block rounded-2xl px-8 py-14 sm:px-16 sm:py-20">
					<div class="mb-6 flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
						<span
							class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-xs tracking-wider"
							style="background: oklch(0.65 0.12 70 / 10%); border: 1px solid oklch(0.65 0.12 70 / 30%); color: oklch(0.65 0.12 70);"
						>
							<span class="inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full" style="background: oklch(0.65 0.12 70); animation: pulse-glow 2.5s ease-in-out infinite;"></span>
							Coming Soon
						</span>
					</div>

					<h1 class="mb-4 text-4xl tracking-wider text-foreground sm:text-5xl">
						332 Labs<span class="blink-cursor">_</span>
					</h1>

					<p class="mx-auto max-w-xl text-base leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
						[Your vision for 332 Labs in one or two sentences. What makes this different from just "the CTF platform with some extra stuff"? What's the ambition here?]
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- What it will be -->
			<section class="mb-10">
				<div class="glass-card rounded-2xl p-8 sm:p-10">
					<p class="section-label">The Vision</p>
					<h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl tracking-wider text-foreground">What it will be<span class="blink-cursor">_</span></h2>
					<div class="space-y-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground sm:text-base">
						<p>
							[The broader story of 332 Labs — why build a platform, what problem it solves, what it will enable that doesn't exist yet. Be concrete.]
						</p>
						<p>
							[Who is 332 Labs for? Just 332 members? Open to the public? Somewhere in between? How will access work?]
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<!-- Planned features -->
			<section class="mb-10">
				<p class="section-label mb-6">Planned Features</p>
				<div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">

					<div class="glass-card rounded-2xl p-6">
						<div class="mb-3 flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-xl glass-button text-muted-foreground">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M4 15s1-1 4-1 5 2 8 2 4-1 4-1V3s-1 1-4 1-5-2-8-2-4 1-4 1z"/><line x1="4" x2="4" y1="22" y2="15"/></svg>
						</div>
						<h3 class="mb-2 text-base tracking-wider text-foreground">CTF Integration</h3>
						<p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
							[How the existing CTF platform integrates into Labs — will it be embedded, linked, rebuilt? Better account management? Team features? Challenge authoring tools?]
						</p>
					</div>

					<div class="glass-card rounded-2xl p-6">
						<div class="mb-3 flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-xl glass-button text-muted-foreground">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M2 3h6a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v14a3 3 0 0 0-3-3H2z"/><path d="M22 3h-6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v14a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h7z"/></svg>
						</div>
						<h3 class="mb-2 text-base tracking-wider text-foreground">Courses</h3>
						<p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
							[What kind of courses? Who writes them? What topics? How will they be structured — video, text, interactive labs? Will they be free or paid?]
						</p>
					</div>

					<div class="glass-card rounded-2xl p-6">
						<div class="mb-3 flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-xl glass-button text-muted-foreground">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m22 8-6 4 6 4V8z"/><rect width="14" height="12" x="2" y="6" rx="2" ry="2"/></svg>
						</div>
						<h3 class="mb-2 text-base tracking-wider text-foreground">Video Content</h3>
						<p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
							[What video content — walkthroughs, tutorials, talks, recorded events? Who produces it? Where will it live?]
						</p>
					</div>

					<div class="glass-card rounded-2xl p-6">
						<div class="mb-3 flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-xl glass-button text-muted-foreground">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2a3 3 0 0 0-3 3v7a3 3 0 0 0 6 0V5a3 3 0 0 0-3-3z"/><path d="M19 10v2a7 7 0 0 1-14 0v-2"/><line x1="12" x2="12" y1="19" y2="22"/></svg>
						</div>
						<h3 class="mb-2 text-base tracking-wider text-foreground">Audio Content</h3>
						<p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
							[What audio content — podcasts, recordings, voice sessions? Who's involved? What's the format?]
						</p>
					</div>

					<div class="glass-card rounded-2xl p-6">
						<div class="mb-3 flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-xl glass-button text-muted-foreground">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 8V4H8"/><rect width="16" height="12" x="4" y="8" rx="2"/><path d="M2 14h2"/><path d="M20 14h2"/><path d="M15 13v2"/><path d="M9 13v2"/></svg>
						</div>
						<h3 class="mb-2 text-base tracking-wider text-foreground">Telos Integration</h3>
						<p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
							[How Telos will connect to Labs — authentication, notifications, command shortcuts, accessing Labs content from Discord.]
						</p>
					</div>

					<div class="glass-card rounded-2xl p-6">
						<div class="mb-3 flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-xl glass-button text-muted-foreground">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="M12 5v14"/></svg>
						</div>
						<h3 class="mb-2 text-base tracking-wider text-foreground">[More to Come]</h3>
						<p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
							[Anything else on the roadmap that doesn't fit the categories above — tools, profiles, communities within the platform, etc.]
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<!-- Timeline -->
			<section class="mb-10">
				<div class="glass-card rounded-2xl p-8 sm:p-10">
					<p class="section-label">Roadmap</p>
					<h2 class="mb-6 text-2xl tracking-wider text-foreground">Timeline<span class="blink-cursor">_</span></h2>
					<div class="relative space-y-6 pl-6">
						<div class="absolute left-0 top-2 bottom-2 w-px bg-white/8"></div>
						{[
							{ phase: 'Phase 1', label: '[Q/Year]', desc: '[What gets built first — foundation, auth, core platform. What does MVP look like?]' },
							{ phase: 'Phase 2', label: '[Q/Year]', desc: '[What comes after — CTF integration, first courses, initial content library.]' },
							{ phase: 'Phase 3', label: '[Q/Year]', desc: '[Full feature rollout — video platform, audio, full Telos integration, wider access.]' },
							{ phase: 'Launch', label: '[Target date]', desc: '[What launch looks like — beta, soft launch, full public/member launch.]' },
						].map(item => (
							<div class="relative">
								<div class="absolute -left-[1.4rem] top-1.5 h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full glass-button border border-white/20"></div>
								<div class="text-xs tracking-widest text-muted-foreground uppercase mb-1">{item.phase} · {item.label}</div>
								<p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">{item.desc}</p>
							</div>
						))}
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<!-- Waitlist / notification -->
			<section>
				<div class="glass-card rounded-2xl p-8 text-center sm:p-12">
					<h2 class="mb-3 text-2xl tracking-wider text-foreground">Stay in the loop<span class="blink-cursor">_</span></h2>
					<p class="mx-auto mb-8 max-w-md text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
						[How people can stay updated on 332 Labs — is there a waitlist? Do they just watch this page? Follow somewhere? Join the Discord?]
					</p>
					<div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-3">
						<a
							href="[DISCORD_INVITE_URL]"
							class="glass-button glass-button-glass inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-xl px-5 py-2.5 text-sm tracking-wider text-foreground no-underline transition-all"
							target="_blank"
							rel="noopener noreferrer"
						>
							Join Discord for updates
						</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

		</div>
	</div>

	<!-- Footer -->
	<footer class="border-t border-white/5 px-4 py-8">
		<div class="mx-auto flex max-w-4xl flex-col items-center justify-between gap-4 sm:flex-row">
			<div class="flex items-center gap-2.5">
				<img src="/polygon.svg" alt="332" class="h-5 w-5 opacity-60" width="20" height="20" />
				<span class="text-sm tracking-widest text-muted-foreground">332</span>
			</div>
			<div class="flex items-center gap-6 text-xs tracking-wider text-muted-foreground">
				<a href="/" class="hover:text-foreground transition-colors no-underline">Home</a>
				<a href="/projects" class="hover:text-foreground transition-colors no-underline">Projects</a>
				<a href="/blog" class="hover:text-foreground transition-colors no-underline">Blog</a>
			</div>
			<p class="text-xs tracking-wider text-muted-foreground opacity-40">
				© {new Date().getFullYear()} 332
			</p>
		</div>
	</footer>
</PageLayout>
